### Fetch an access token from local Keycloak (client_credentials, scopes books:read + books:write)
# @name clientToken
POST http://localhost:8090/realms/test-realm/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&client_id=test-client&client_secret=test-secret&scope=books:read books:write

> {% client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.access_token); %}

### Fetch a user access token (password grant — alice has books:read)
# @name aliceToken
POST http://localhost:8090/realms/test-realm/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=test-client&client_secret=test-secret&username=alice&password=alice

> {% client.global.set("aliceAccessToken", response.body.access_token); %}

### Fetch a user access token (password grant — bob has books:write)
# @name bobToken
POST http://localhost:8090/realms/test-realm/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=test-client&client_secret=test-secret&username=bob&password=bob

> {% client.global.set("bobAccessToken", response.body.access_token); %}

### List all books (public — no token required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books
Accept: application/json

### Get a single book by id (requires books:read)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create a new book (requires books:write)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "isbn": "978-0134685991",
  "title": "Effective Java",
  "author": "Joshua Bloch",
  "publishedDate": "2017-12-27"
}

### Update an existing book (requires books:write)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "title": "Effective Java (3rd Edition)",
  "author": "Joshua Bloch"
}

### Delete a book (requires books:write)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
